# Supabase Auth email verification:
# - Authentication -> Providers -> Email -> Confirm email: enabled
# - Disable auto-confirm users if it is enabled in your Supabase project
# - Authentication -> Sessions -> JWT expiry: 28800 seconds or lower
# - Authentication -> Emails -> OTP expiry / recovery link expiry: 3600 seconds or lower
# - Password policy: minimum 10 characters, uppercase, lowercase, and number
# - Authentication -> URL Configuration -> Site URL: set to NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL in each environment
# - Add Redirect URLs:
#   http://localhost:3000/auth/callback
#   http://localhost:3000/login
#   http://localhost:3000/update-password
#   https://your-production-domain.com/auth/callback
#   https://your-production-domain.com/login
#   https://your-production-domain.com/update-password

